Permintaan saya tak melampau, kan?

526
00:29:01,520 --> 00:29:02,479
Xiaosu.

527
00:29:03,599 --> 00:29:05,359
Awak tak bagi muka pada saya?

528
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:12,079
Kamu berdua nampak gembira.

529
00:29:13,959 --> 00:29:14,800
Fanlu.

530
00:29:20,479 --> 00:29:21,400
Abang Yuzheng.

531
00:29:21,839 --> 00:29:23,520
Ke mana awak pergi baru-baru ini?

532
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:25,280
Tak jawab panggilan,
