533
00:29:25,439 --> 00:29:26,680
Saya risaukan awak.

534
00:29:28,280 --> 00:29:29,719
Maaf, Pengarah Lei, Pengarah Jiang.

535
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:31,560
Kamu berdua mesti nak berbincang.

536
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:33,599
Saya ada kerja lain, minta diri dulu.

537
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:41,119
Pandang apa lagi, dia dah pergi pun.

538
00:29:42,359 --> 00:29:44,119
Fanlu, awak buat apa di sini?

539
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:46,800
Saya yang patut tanya, Abang Yuzheng.

540
00:29:46,959 --> 00:29:48,319
Awak bos Yu Tian.

541
00:29:48,439 --> 00:29:50,560
Kenapa tiba-tiba awak makan
di kantin kakitangan?

542
00:29:50,839 --> 00:29:52,560
Takkan awak bersimpati
dengan kakitangan?

543
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:53,839
Atau ada sebab lain?

544
00:29:54,599 --> 00:29:57,560
Kenapa saya tak boleh datang
ke kantin kakitangan?

545
00:29:57,839 --> 00:29:59,719
Apa salahnya saya makan tengah hari

546
00:29:59,959 --> 00:30:01,239
