589
00:33:03,239 --> 00:33:04,439
Ya, masuklah.

590
00:33:04,599 --> 00:33:05,560
Nanti.

591
00:33:06,239 --> 00:33:08,719
Kenapa awak tak beritahu saya dulu?

592
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:28,359
Yuzheng, dah lama mak cik tak masak.

593
00:33:28,479 --> 00:33:29,959
Tak tahulah rasanya sedap atau tidak.

594
00:33:30,079 --> 00:33:32,640
Semua ini kegemaran awak, makanlah.

595
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:33,839
Terima kasih, Mak Cik Shao.

596
00:33:34,199 --> 00:33:36,199
Saya sibuk ke sana ke sini setiap hari.

597
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:38,959
Saya rindu rasa ini.

598
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,040
Restoran lain tak setanding.

599
00:33:41,319 --> 00:33:43,319
Ikan kukus yang mak cik masak
paling sedap.

600
00:33:45,599 --> 00:33:46,199
Masa kamu berdua

601
00:33:46,359 --> 00:33:48,199
makan ikan kukus dulu,

602
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:51,239
berebut makan seekor ikan yang sama.

603
00:33:52,239 --> 00:33:53,520
Saya masih ingat budak nakal itu

604
00:33:54,079 --> 00:33:55,719
letakkan tulang ikan di atas meja.

605
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:57,040
Lepas itu, tolak ke depan saya

606
00:33:57,239 --> 00:33:58,479
dan mengadu pada awak.

607
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:00,520
Konon saya yang habiskan ikan kukus itu.

608
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:02,000
Dia tak dapat makan.

609
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:04,119
Masa kecil, kamu berdua

610
00:34:04,280 --> 00:34:06,119
bagai belangkas ke sana ke mari bersama.

611
00:34:06,479 --> 00:34:08,600
Jiran-jiran pun takut tengok kamu.

612
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:10,520
Selalu juga buat mak cik risau.

613
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:19,760
Mak Cik Shao, mak cik baru sembuh,

614
00:34:19,919 --> 00:34:20,919
