Macam mana saya nak cakap ya?

682
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:24,399
Saya nak beritahu awak.

683
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:28,080
Abang Li, janganlah naikkan sewa kami.

684
00:38:28,399 --> 00:38:30,520
